 ♫ Summer cherries are a bit cool ♫ 

75
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:39,616
 ♫ I gaze from afar ♫ 

76
00:06:39,616 --> 00:06:42,496
 ♫ The unspoken wishes of that year ♫ 

77
00:06:42,496 --> 00:06:45,632
 ♫ Familiar shadows lengthen ♫ 

78
00:06:45,632 --> 00:06:47,424
 ♫ Beyond sight ♫ 

79
00:06:47,424 --> 00:06:51,556
 ♫ Your silhouette is so gentle ♫ 

80
00:06:51,556 --> 00:06:55,520
 ♫ The world is spinning ♫ 

81
00:06:57,280 --> 00:07:01,248
 ♫ The breeze is shouting ♫ 

82
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:06,720
 ♫ The scenery in amber ♫ 

83
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:10,048
 ♫ Clear as yesterday ♫ 

84
00:07:10,048 --> 00:07:11,456
 ♫ Reality is in front of me ♫ 

85
00:07:11,456 --> 00:07:15,712
 ♫ The future folds in the palm ♫ 

86
00:07:15,712 --> 00:07:21,472
 ♫ You're the key to who I am ♫ 

87
00:07:21,472 --> 00:07:26,688
 ♫ Accompany me to become myself ♫ 

88
00:07:26,688 --> 00:07:29,664
 ♫ The night is long ♫ 

89
00:07:29,664 --> 00:07:32,448
 ♫ My stubbornness grows wildly ♫ 

90
00:07:32,448 --> 00:07:34,624
 ♫ I can't stop running ♫ 

91
